          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--cream);border-radius:8px;padding:0.75rem 1.25rem;">
            <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.58rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage2);margin-bottom:2px;">Logotype</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--forest);">Wordmark "mahathi"</div>
          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--cream);border-radius:8px;padding:0.75rem 1.25rem;">
            <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.58rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage2);margin-bottom:2px;">Full Lockup</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--forest);">Symbol + Logotype</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Core Values</div>
    <div class="section-divider" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;"></div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i></div>
        <div class="value-number">01 — Integrity</div>
        <div class="value-title">Unwavering Trust</div>
        <p class="value-body">In insurance, trust is the product. We earn it through transparency, consistency, and a refusal to cut corners — in our technology, our relationships, and our communication.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-cpu"></i></div>
        <div class="value-number">02 — Precision</div>
        <div class="value-title">Intelligent Accuracy</div>
        <p class="value-body">Insurance decisions carry real consequences. Our platforms are built to the highest standards of data accuracy and process fidelity, because precision is not a feature — it is the foundation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i></div>
        <div class="value-number">03 — Impact</div>
        <div class="value-title">Measurable Outcomes</div>
        <p class="value-body">We measure our success by our clients' results. Every solution we deploy is designed to produce quantifiable improvements in efficiency, accuracy, and business performance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-people"></i></div>
        <div class="value-number">04 — Partnership</div>
        <div class="value-title">Deep Collaboration</div>
        <p class="value-body">We don't hand over software and disappear. We embed alongside our clients, learning their systems, understanding their constraints, and delivering solutions that actually work in practice.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat"></i></div>
        <div class="value-number">05 — Innovation</div>
        <div class="value-title">Continuous Evolution</div>
        <p class="value-body">Insurance technology is not static. We invest relentlessly in research, architecture evolution, and emerging technology — ensuring our clients always operate on the forward edge of capability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon"><i class="bi bi-globe2"></i></div>
        <div class="value-number">06 — Clarity</div>
        <div class="value-title">Complex Made Clear</div>
        <p class="value-body">We translate the language of enterprise technology into the language of insurance outcomes — making sophisticated systems understandable, manageable, and valuable at every organizational level.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section> -->

