  <!-- ═══ LOGO CLEARSPACE ═══ -->
  <section class="brand-section section-anchor" id="logo-clearspace" style="background-color: #e3e6e0;">
    <div class="section-label">— Logo Integrity</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Clearspace &amp; Sizing</h2>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <p class="section-intro">The logo must always be surrounded by sufficient clear space — a protected zone free of text, graphics, and competing visual elements. This breathing room is not optional: it maintains the mark's authority, legibility, and visual impact in every context.</p>

    <!-- Clearspace Demo -->
    <div class="clearspace-demo">
      <div class="clearspace-inner">
        <div class="clearspace-box"></div>
        <!-- Clearspace measurement labels -->
        <div class="clearspace-label" style="top:-52px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);">← x →  Clear space = height of "m"</div>
        <div class="clearspace-label" style="left:-130px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%) rotate(-90deg);transform-origin:center;">x — minimum</div>
        <img
          src="data:image/png;base64,"
          alt="Mahathi logo"
          class="img-fluid"
          style="max-width:520px;width:100%;height:auto;"
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--sage2);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:2.5rem;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:1px;">The minimum clear space on all four sides equals the cap height of the lowercase "m" in the wordmark. No other graphic elements, text, or imagery may enter this zone. On digital interfaces, increase clear space generously.</p>

    <!-- Sizing Guidance -->
    <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Minimum Size Guidance</div>
    <div class="section-divider" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;"></div>
    <div class="sizing-grid">
      <div class="sizing-card">
        <div class="sizing-preview">
          <img
          src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
          alt="Mahathi logo"
          class="img-fluid"
          style="max-width:250px;width:100%;height:auto;"
        >
