        >
        </div>
        <div class="rule-meta">
          <div class="rule-title">Use on approved backgrounds</div>
          <div class="rule-desc">Always place the logo on Cream (#EEF0EC), Forest Green (#253830), or White. These are the only approved background surfaces.</div>
        </div>
      </div>




      <!-- DON'T 1 — tilted (Don't 1 SVG) -->
      <div class="dont-card">
        <div class="rule-preview" style="background:var(--cream2);">
          <span class="rule-badge badge-dont">✗ Don't</span>
          <img
          src="data:image/png;base64,"
          alt="Mahathi logo"
          class="img-fluid"
          style="max-width:540px;width:100%;height:auto;"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="rule-meta">
          <div class="rule-title">Never rotate or tilt the logo</div>
          <div class="rule-desc">The logo must always appear horizontally. Rotation destroys optical balance and communicates instability — the opposite of our brand promise.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- DON'T 2 — wrong brand color (#31EB3E) -->
      <div class="dont-card">
        <div class="rule-preview" style="background:var(--cream2);">
          <span class="rule-badge badge-dont">✗ Don't</span>
          <img
          src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
          alt="Mahathi logo"
          class="img-fluid"
          style="max-width:540px;width:100%;height:auto;"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="rule-meta">
          <div class="rule-title">Never recolor with unapproved colors</div>
          <div class="rule-desc">Do not substitute neon, fluorescent, or off-brand colors. Only the approved palette (#76A379 Sage, #EEF0EC Cream, or #253830 Forest) may be used.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- DON'T 3 — drop shadow -->
      <div class="dont-card">
        <div class="rule-preview" style="background:var(--cream2);">
          <span class="rule-badge badge-dont">✗ Don't</span>
          <img
          src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
          alt="Mahathi logo"
          class="img-fluid"
          style="max-width:540px;width:100%;height:auto;"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="rule-meta">
          <div class="rule-title">Never add drop shadows or effects</div>
          <div class="rule-desc">CSS filters, drop shadows, glows, and texture overlays corrupt the mark's precision. The logo must always appear clean and unmodified.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- DON'T 4 — stretched/distorted -->
      <div class="dont-card">
        <div class="rule-preview" style="background:var(--cream2);">
          <span class="rule-badge badge-dont">✗ Don't</span>
          <img
          src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
          alt="Mahathi logo"
          class="img-fluid"
          style="max-width:540px;width:100%;height:auto;"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="rule-meta">
          <div class="rule-title">Never distort or stretch the logo</div>
          <div class="rule-desc">Scale uniformly, preserving the original aspect ratio. Stretching or squashing destroys the geometric integrity of the mark.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- DON'T 5 — stretched/distorted -->
      <div class="dont-card">
        <div class="rule-preview" style="background:var(--cream2);">
          <span class="rule-badge badge-dont">✗ Don't</span>
          <img
          src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
